atar chicken drumsticks hot with a generous side of cucumber herb slaw. Drizzle extra olive oil over the slaw or add a squeeze of fresh lemon if desired.\n\n','\n',char(10)),'["6 chicken drumsticks (about 1Â½ lbs)","2 Tbsp butter, melted","1 Tbsp dried oregano","1 Tbsp sesame seeds","2 tsp ground sumac","1 tsp dried thyme","Â½ tsp garlic powder","Â½ tsp smoked paprika","Â½ tsp sea salt","Â¼ tsp black pepper","1 cup cucumber, julienned or thinly sliced","Â¼ cup red onion, thinly sliced","2 Tbsp fresh parsley, chopped","2 Tbsp fresh mint, chopped","1 Tbsp lemon juice","1 Tbsp olive oil","Â¼ tsp sea salt","Â¼ tsp black pepper"]',NULL,NULL,NULL,'team_default','public');
